Using tailwind v4.0.0.25

```scss
@import "tailwindcss/preflight" layer(base);
@import "../components/_index.scss" layer(components);
```
In the images below you can see that the font styles are being overridden bij the tailwind preflight

<img width="333" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3ea9d2c9-c6ee-49be-9d5d-84ef82ef4b68">

